---

---

<section id="sobre-nosotros" class="py-24 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
            <div class="relative" data-aos="fade-right">
                <!-- Decorative background elements -->
                <div
                    class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-24 h-24 bg-blue-100 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-xl opacity-70 animate-blob"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="absolute -bottom-8 -right-8 w-24 h-24 bg-purple-100 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-xl opacity-70 animate-blob animation-delay-2000"
                >
                </div>

                <!-- Image Container -->
                <div
                    class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl skew-y-3 transform transition-transform hover:skew-y-0 duration-500 group"
                >
                    <div class="aspect-4/5 w-full bg-slate-100">
                        <img
                            src="/stefanoprofile.webp"
                            alt="Stefano Andreani"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105"
                            loading="lazy"
                        />
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Floating Card -->
                <div
                    class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-slate-100 max-w-xs transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform cursor-default z-10"
                >
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <div
                            class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white"
                        >
                            <svg
                                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke-width="1.5"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                class="w-6 h-6"
                            >
                                <path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    d="M15.59 14.37a6 6 0 01-5.84 7.38v-4.8m5.84-2.58a14.98 14.98 0 006.16-12.12A14.98 14.98 0 009.631 8.41m5.96 5.96a14.926 14.926 0 01-5.841 2.58m-.119-8.54a6 6 0 00-7.381 5.84h4.8m2.581-5.84a14.927 14.927 0 00-2.58 5.84m2.699 2.7c-.103.021-.207.041-.311.06a15.09 15.09 0 01-2.448-2.448 14.9 14.9 0 01.06-.312m-2.24 2.39a4.493 4.493 0 00-1.757 4.306 4.493 4.493 0 004.306-1.758M16.5 9a1.5 1.5 0 11-3 0 1.5 1.5 0 013 0z"
                                ></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">
                                Más que un coach
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">
                                Un aliado en tu carrera
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-8" data-aos="fade-left">
                <span
                    class="text-blue-600 font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase text-xs border border-blue-100 bg-blue-50 px-3 py-1 rounded-full"
                >
                    Stefano y el Equipo
                </span>

                <h2
                    class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 leading-tight"
                >
                    No somos una corporación fría. <br />
                    <span
                        class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-linear-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600"
                        >Somos tus mentores.</span
                    >
                </h2>

                <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                    <p>
                        ¿Te sientes estancado enviando CVs que nadie lee? Lo
                        entendemos. Hemos estado ahí y hemos ayudado a
                        <strong>más de 50 profesionales</strong> a salir de ese ciclo
                        de frustración.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        En <strong>Somos Empleables</strong>, liderado por
                        Stefano Andreani, no te damos fórmulas mágicas
                        genéricas. Te damos una estrategia probada, herramientas
                        de inteligencia artificial exclusivas y, sobre todo, el
                        acompañamiento humano que necesitas para recuperar la
                        confianza y conquistar el puesto que mereces.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="pt-4 flex gap-4">
                    <a
                        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/stefano-andreani/"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                        class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors"
                    >
                        <svg
                            class="w-5 h-5"
                            fill="currentColor"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            aria-hidden="true"
                            ><path
                                d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"
                            ></path></svg
                        >
                        Conecta con Stefano
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
